Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:04.03,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Mám moc práce s vedením layoutů pro osmou epizodu.{I'm spent from doing the layout \Nsupervision for episode eight.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.65,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Musíš jí to odplatit.{You need to pay her back.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:08.40,Shirobako_Main,endou,0,0,0,,Říkal jsem ti, že s tim žádnej dluh ani odplácení nesouvisí.{I told you, owing and paying back \Nhave nothing to do with it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.67,Shirobako_Main,endou,0,0,0,,Jsem si jistej, že Segawa stejně\Nnemá ráda chlápky jako jsem já.{I'm pretty sure Segawa-san \Ndoesn't like guys like me, either.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.50,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Segawa řekla to samé.{Segawa-san said the exact same thing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.00,Shirobako_Main,end,0,0,0,,He?{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:18.51,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Říkala, že si nemyslí, že ji máte rád.{She was saying that she \Ndidn't think you liked her.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.97,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Bála se, protože všechno kreslila ve spěchu.{She was worried since she \Ndrew everything in such a rush.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:24.43,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Ale to ne… Vlastně mě Segawa nadchla tím,{Er, no... I was actually \Nimpressed with Segawa-san}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.42,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,že zvládla tak kvalitní snímky za tak krátkou dobu!{for producing such quality \Nin that amount of time.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.89,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Ale nejsou dostatečně třpitivý{dostatečně křiklavý?}, co?{But it's not flashy enough.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.52,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Proč si to musel vyžvanit?!{Why do you have to say that?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:32.73,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Když to uděláte, koupím vám\Nvšechny donuty z Pekka Donuts.{If you accept, I will buy \Nyou some Pekka donuts.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.44,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Sladkosti moc nemusim.{I don't like sweet things.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.84,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Tak co třeba něco hořkého?{What about bitter things?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.76,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Co máš na mysli?{What do you mean by bitter things?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:39.88,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,A co třeba něco piktantního?{What about spicy things?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.12,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,O to nejde!\N Jídlo nechci.{That's not the point! \NI'm not interested in food.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.06,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Co teda? Moc? Slávu?{Power, then? Fame?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.94,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,A to mi jako dokážeš sehnat?{You're going to get those for me?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:46.63,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Budu se snažit!{O'll do my best!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.28,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Já to nechci!{I don't want it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.79,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Dobrá. Udělám to.{All right, fine. I'll do it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.79,Shirobako_Ep_Title_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Arupin je tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.19,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Arupin je tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.17,Marukawa_Masahito_03:56_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Marukawa Masahito \N{\fs22.5}Prezident
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.65,Shirobako_Main,all,0,0,0,,Dobré ráno!{Good morning!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.17,Shirobako_Main,boss,0,0,0,,Ano, dobré ráno.{Yes, good morning.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.69,Shirobako_Main,ochi,0,0,0,,Takže, v 11 ráno začíná{So, starting at 11 AM, we have the}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.91,Shirobako_Main,ochi,0,0,0,,kontrola 3D a částečná kontrola denice 6. epizody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.37,Shirobako_Main,erika,0,0,0,,Natáčení pro sedmou epizodu začíná v 1 odpoledne.{Filming for episode seven \Nis set to begin at 1 PM.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:11.59,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Třetí epizoda, kterou mám na starost, dneska dokončí střih,{Episode three, which I am in \Ncharge of, has video editing today,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.63,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,a pak bude doručena!{and then all goods should be delivered!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:16.08,Shirobako_Main,boss,0,0,0,,Ó, dobrá práce.{Oh, well done.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.65,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Pracoval jsem na tom tak tvrdě!{I worked so hard!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:21.49,Honda_Yutaka_04:17_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Honda Jutaka \N{\fs22.5}Production Desk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:21.49,Shirobako_Main,honda,0,0,0,,Um, dokončení jen o tři dny dříve, když jsme teprve u třetí epizody fakt normální není.{Um, delivery three days prior when \Nwe're only on episode three isn't normal.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.36,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,He? Není dokončení tři dny předem docela úsporný?{Huh? Isn't three days before pretty efficient?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.36,Takanashi_Tarou_04:21_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Takanaši Taró\N{\fs22.5}Produkční asistent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:28.08,Shirobako_Main,yano,0,0,0,,Na začátku byl náš cíl mít všechny epizody dva týdny dopředu.{We were shooting for two weeks prior \Nfor all the episodes of}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:28.08,Yano_Erika_04:24_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Jano Erika \N{\fs22.5}Produkční asistentka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.26,Shirobako_Main,ochi,0,0,0,,1. epizoda byla dva týdny dopředu,\N 2. epizoda jeden…{Episode one was two weeks prior, \Nepisode two was one week prior,,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.98,Ochiai_Tatsuya_04:28_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,376)}Očiai Tacuja\N{\fs22.5}Produkční asistent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.85,Shirobako_Main,ochi,0,0,0,,a třetí epizoda bude jen o tři dny napřed.{and episode three is three days prior...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.21,Shirobako_Main,ochi,0,0,0,,Takhle se epizody čtyři už nikdy nedočkáme…{At this rate, episode four \Nonward is going to be hell.}{fixme}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:39.09,Miyamori_Aoi_04:35_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,376)}Mijamori Aoi \N{\fs22.5}Produkční asistentka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.12,Shirobako_Main,honda,0,0,0,,Mijamori, jak to jde s natáčením pro čtvrtou epizodu?{Miyamori-san, how's the filming \Ngoing for episode four?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.73,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Postárám se, aby to dnes bylo hotové.{I'll make sure it's done by today.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:41.92,Shirobako_Main,boss,0,0,0,,Hodně štěstí.{Do your best.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:45.80,Watanabe_Shun_04:41_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,376)}Watanabe Džun \N{\fs22.5}Produkční manažer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.72,Shirobako_Main,nabe,0,0,0,,Mám setkání v Šindžuku. V 11 večer budu zpátky.{I have a meeting in Shinjuku. \NI'll be back at 11 PM.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.59,Shirobako_Main,boss,0,0,0,,Doufám, že dnes vyhrajete.{I hope you win today.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:50.62,Shirobako_Main,lady,0,0,0,,Prosím odneste si jakýkoliv osobní majetek, co zůstal v Zasedací místnosti č. 2{Please clear out any personal \Nbelongings left in Meeting Room 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:51.47,Okitsu_Yuka_04:47_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,376)}Okicu Juka \N{\fs22.5}{General Manager}Hlavní manažerka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.48,Shirobako_Main,lady,0,0,0,,do konce dnešního dne.{y the end of today.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.73,Shirobako_Main,lady,0,0,0,,Toť vše.{That is all.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.80,Yasuhara_Ema_05:19_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Jasuhara Ema \N{\fs22.5}Key Animator
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.97,Shirobako_Main,ema,0,0,0,,Á, Zuko? Máš teď chvilku?{Ah, Zuka-chan? Can you talk right now?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.48,Shirobako_Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Nemusela si mi volat zpátky.{You didn't have to go through \Nthe trouble of calling me back.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.87,Shirobako_Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Ale díky. Jo, jak to jde v práci?{Thank you, though. Yeah. How's work?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:42.94,Shirobako_Italics,ema,0,0,0,,No, stačí prostě dělat to, co mám před sebou.{It's taking everything I have to finish \Nthe work that's right in front of me.}{fixme}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.02,Shirobako_Italics,ema,0,0,0,,Zdá se mi, že Oi to má mnohem těžší.{Oi-chan seems to have it tougher than me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.07,Shirobako_Italics,ema,0,0,0,,V práci se ani moc nepotkáváme.{We only see each other in passing at work.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:50.38,Shirobako_Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Wow! Vypadá to, že jste dost zaneprázdněný.{Wow! It sounds like you're really busy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.15,Shirobako_Italics,ema,0,0,0,,Má teď na starosti jak epizodu čtyři, tak i epizodu devět…{She has both episode four and \Nepisode nine right now, so...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:55.50,Shirobako_Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Nemůžeš jí nějak pomoci?{You can't help her at all?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.96,Shirobako_Main,ema,0,0,0,,Práce animátorky je o dost jiná, než je práce produkční.{The animator's job is totally \Ndifferent from production's job.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:02.00,Shirobako_Main,ema,0,0,0,,Ale kdybych se zlepšila, tak bych jí\Nmožná mohla trochu pomoct…{If I got better, I might be able to help a little...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.33,Shirobako_Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Chápu… No, je to práce.{I see... Well, I guess it is work.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.51,Shirobako_Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Není to jako když jsme dělali seriály v klubu.{It's not like when we were in our club.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.71,Shirobako_Italics,ema,0,0,0,,A jak se máš, Zuko?{How are you, Zuka-chan?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.67,Shirobako_Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Oh, jo. To ti řeknu jindy.{Ah, yeah... I'll tell you later.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:13.72,Shirobako_Main,shizu,0,0,0,,Ale to setkání tenhle měsíc furt platí, že?{We're all still getting together \Nonce this month, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.91,Shirobako_Main,ema,0,0,0,,Jo. Připomenu to Mí a Rí.{Yeah. I'll remind Mii and Rii-chan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.49,Shirobako_Italics,shizu,0,0,0,,OK! Zatím!{Okay, see you later.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:24.11,Sugie_Shigeru_06:20_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Sugie Šigeru \N{\fs22.5}Animátor klíčových snímků
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.11,Shirobako_Main,sugi,0,0,0,,Odcházím.{I'm heading out.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:25.37,Shirobako_Main,ema,0,0,0,,Eh? Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.10,Shirobako_Main,ema,0,0,0,,Na shledanou.{Thank you for your hard work.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:38.54,Kinoshita_Seiichi_06:34_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,376)}Kinošita Seiiči \N{\fs22.5}Režisér
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.25,Shirobako_Main,aru,0,0,0,,Dobré ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.04,Shirobako_Main,aya,0,0,0,,Dobré ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.42,Shirobako_Main,akane,0,0,0,,Dobré ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:44.41,Shirobako_Main,aru,0,0,0,,Wow! Rejža kreslí storyboardy.\NKterá to je epizoda?{Wow! The director is drawing storyboards. \NWhat episode is that?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.09,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Finální.{The final episode.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.43,Shirobako_Main,akane,0,0,0,,Co se na konci stane?{What happens in the end?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.01,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Co myslíte, že by se mělo stát?{What do you think should happen?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.02,Inanami_Yoshikazu_06:53_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Inanami Yošikazu \N{\fs22.5}Zvukový režisér
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:57.02,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Takže, kdy budou ty storyboardy?{So when will the storyboards be finished?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.24,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No, nejsem si jistej.{Well, I'm not sure.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.52,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Myslím, že první část bude \Nněkdy na konci měsíce.{I think the A part will be done \Nby the end of this month.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.52,Shirobako_Main,Person,0,0,0,,Cože?! Ježiš, rejžo!{What? Come on, Director!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:05.40,Kazushiro_Koutarou_07:01_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,376)}Kazushiro Koutarou \N{\fs22.5}Maker Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.86,Shirobako_Main,Person,0,0,0,,Už se nemůžeme furt zdržovat!{We can't delay the delivery any further.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:10.28,Yamabuchi_Atsushi_07:06_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,376)}Yamabuči Atsuši \N{\fs22.5}{Mixer}Zvukař
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.13,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,S vašim minulym projektem jste si prošel peklo.{You went through hell with \Nthe last project you worked on.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.58,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Měl byste se z toho poučit.{You need to learn your lesson.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:11.91,Shirobako_Main,mixer,0,0,0,,Má recht.{That's very true.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.64,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,I já jsem za to dostal vynadáno. {Even I ended up getting \Nyelled at for that. I'm over it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:15.70,Fuji_Asuka_07:11_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Fudži Asuka \N{\fs22.5}Mixing Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:15.70,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Moc se omlouvám!{I'm so sorry!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:19.58,Nakata_Eri_07:15_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,376)}Nakata Eri \N{\fs22.5}Zvuková producentka
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.60,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Ha, já vim! To bylo {\i1}Jiggly Jiggly{\i0}...{fixme}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.36,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Pššt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.54,Shirobako_Main,person,0,0,0,,Všichni jsou tu.{Everyone is here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.84,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(134,25)\fade(500,500)}Doslovný překlad: Éééééééééééééé
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.84,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,No, tak tedy…{Well, then...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.17,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Dneska zahájíme nahrávání pro epizodu osm.{We'll be conducting the after-recording \Nfor Exodus episode eight today.}{fixme}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.04,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Díky všem, že jste přišli.{Thank you all for coming.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.67,Shirobako_Main,all,0,0,0,,Děkujeme.{fixme}{Thank you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.19,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Tohle je Nakaharu Mei a hraje Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.93,Nakaharu_Mei_07:28_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Nakaharu Mei \N{\fs22.5}Hraje Akane
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.89,Shirobako_Main,akane,0,0,0,,Zdravím.{Thank you for having me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.20,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Tohle je Itó Suzuka a hraje Ayu.{This is Itou Suzuka-san, who plays Aya.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:37.06,Itou_Suzuka_07:33_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Itó Suzuka \N{\fs22.5}Hraje Ayu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.67,Shirobako_Main,aya,0,0,0,,Zdravím.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.68,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Tohle je Kajana Mui, která hraje Arupinu.{This is Kayana Mui-san, who plays Arupin.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:40.64,Kayana_Mui_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Kajana Mui \N{\fs22.5}Hraje Arupinu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.64,Shirobako_Main,aru,0,0,0,,Zdravím.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.27,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Dobrá začneme první částí.{Okay, we'll start with the A part.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.81,Shirobako_Main,person,0,0,0,,{Rolling.}Jedem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:51.09,Shirobako_Main,akane,0,0,0,,To sice jo, ale teď stejně nemůžem nic dělat.{You say that, but there's \Nnothing we can do now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.61,Shirobako_Main,aya,0,0,0,,No, tak co podle tebe máme dělat?!{Then what are we going to do?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:56.21,Shirobako_Main,aya,0,0,0,,Jen to, že víme, že s tím nic nemůžeme dělat, nestačí!{Just knowing it can't be helped \Nisn't going to help anything!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.08,Shirobako_Main,akane,0,0,0,,A čí si myslíš, že je to chyba?!{Just whose fault are you saying it is?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.66,Shirobako_Main,aru,0,0,0,,Víte, cukrová vata…{You know, cotton candy...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:01.50,Shirobako_Main,both,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:05.88,Shirobako_Main,aru,0,0,0,,…cukrová vata do druhýho rána vždycky zmizí.\NNevíte proč?{...always disappears by the \Nnext morning. Why is that?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.31,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Nó, u té části s cukrovou vatou…{Hmm, for the cotton candy part...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:12.52,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Mohla bys to říct tak, aby to vyznělo jako, že ti na tom víc záleží?{Instead of sounding like an airhead,\Nmaybe make it sound a little more urgent?}{fixme}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.31,Shirobako_Main,aru,0,0,0,,Dobrá.{All right.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.01,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Zatímco zanecháš i kus té stupidity,{While keeping the airhead thing in mind,}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:19.17,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,prosím dej na povrch pocity, kterými je chceš uklidnit, aby se nehádali.{please bring out her feelings of wanting \Nto stop their argument a little more.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:22.95,Shirobako_Main,aru,0,0,0,,Mám tedy znít i trochu víc nadšeně?{Should I sound a little more \Nexcited when I say it, then?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.40,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,No…{Well...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:28.08,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Zadržovat nadšenost úplně je taky možnost…\NCo z toho vybereme?{Holding it back completely is an option, \Nas well, but... What should we go with?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.20,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Co myslíte vy, režisére?{What do you think, Director?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.63,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Hm… Myslím, že nadšenost{Hmm... I think being excited}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.48,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,zní víc jako Arupin, ano.{sounds more like Arupin.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.74,Madoka_Hironori_08:33_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,376)}Madoka Hironori \N{\fs22.5}Režisér animace
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.69,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Co myslíš, Madoku?{What do you think, Madoka?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.41,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Snaží se udržet, {She's holding back,}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.74,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,ale její nadšenost se stejně prodírá ven, třeba?{but her excitement is showing through, maybe?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.95,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Tohle bych rád slyšel.{I'd like to hear that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.97,Shirobako_Main,arupin,0,0,0,,Víte, cukrová vata…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.93,Shirobako_Main,arupin,0,0,0,,…do druhýho rána vždycky zmizí.\NNevíte proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.17,Shirobako_Main,arupin,0,0,0,,Víte, cukrová vata…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:53.33,Shirobako_Main,arupin,0,0,0,,…do druhýho rána vždycky zmizí.\NNevíte proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.26,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Jo, to zní lépe.{I think that's more like it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.51,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Dobrá, teď nahrajeme první část naostro.{All right, we're going to start \Nthe real take of the A part.}
