Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.31,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Chlape, dabérky jsou tak hustý.{Man, voice actors are so good.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.30,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Děláš jako kdybys tu byl novej.{What are you? New?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.71,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,No ale neni to užasný?!{But isn't it amazing?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.86,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Prostě bum! A najednou změní hlas podle toho, jak jim řeknou.{They can just be like, bam! \NAnd change their voice as directed.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.89,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,No jasně, to je jejich práce. To z toho sereš až teď?{That's their job. You're \Ngetting excited over it now?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.04,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Úplně zbožňuju tu Arupin.{I'm all about Arupin, myself.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.71,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Dám si říct i od starších.{I'm totally okay with older chicks.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:25.64,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Ježiši…{Seriously...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.61,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Madoku,{Madoka-san,}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:29.04,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,nevíš jak vybírají dabérky?{do you know how they pick voice actors?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.15,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Konkurzy.{Auditions.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.97,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,A byl si u nějakého?{Have you ever seen one?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:34.55,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Ne. To je jen pro režiséra a jiný vyšší pozice.{No. That's only for the director and higher.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.28,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Já bych se rád na konkurz podíval.\NTo by bylo hustý.{That'd be awesome! \NI totally want to see one.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.35,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Ty si idiot. Slyšel jsem, že to neni nic lehkýho.{You're an idiot. I heard it's really rough.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:42.47,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Musíš celej den poslouchat stovky lidí říkat tu samou větu.{You have to listen to a hundred people \Nsay the same lines in a single day.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:46.10,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Vážně?! To se setkáš se stovkama dabérek?!{Seriously?! You get to meet \Na hundred voice actors?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.14,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,To je skvělý!{That's awesome!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:50.15,Exodus!_09:47_(Ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Exodus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.57,Shirobako_Italics,akane,0,0,0,,Cože? Proč?!{What? Why?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.56,Shirobako_Italics,aya,0,0,0,,Ne, to nemůže být pravda! Nemůže!{No, it can't be true! It can't be!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.62,Shirobako_Italics,aya,0,0,0,,Řekni, že to není pravda!{Tell me it's not true!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:02.62,Shirobako_Italics,akane,0,0,0,,Sestřičko, je to pravda? Nebo si z nás jen utahuješ?{Is it true? Were you really tricking us, Onee-san?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.50,Shirobako_Italics,aya,0,0,0,,A komu teď vůbec máme věřit?{Who are we supposed to believe now?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.14,Shirobako_Italics,aru,0,0,0,,Věděla jsem to.{I knew it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:13.45,Shirobako_Italics,aru,0,0,0,,Věděla jsem, že {I knew that}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:17.22,Shirobako_Italics,aru,0,0,0,,sestřička patří k Gingerům.{Onee-san belonged to Ginger.}{fixme: sestra, sestřička^^^^^^few lines above}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.34,Shirobako_Italics,aru,0,0,0,,Věděla jsem to!{I knew it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:23.35,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ten zvuk dveří na střihu 210…{About the door sound at cut 210...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.91,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Rád bych, aby ty dveře měly těžší zvuk.{I'd like to make it sound heavier.}
