Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:26.99,Shirobako_Main,fx,0,0,0,,Dobrá.{Okay.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.74,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,{A little heavier.}Trochu těžší.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.53,Shirobako_Main,fx,0,0,0,,Přehraju pár různých.{I'll play a few different ones.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.08,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Jo, to je ono.{Oh, that's the one.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.07,Shirobako_Main,fx,0,0,0,,Dobrá, mám to.{Got it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.63,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,A taky, Inanami, tu hudbu…{Also, Inanami-san, about the music...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:42.08,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,…na střihu 248 bych trochu pozměnil.{At 248, I'd like to change it a little.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.65,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Jakým směrem?{In what direction?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.64,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:49.04,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,No, teď spíš sedí k náladě,\N takže byste byl radši, aby seděl k situaci?{Right now, it's set more to the mood, \Nbut would you prefer it set to the situation?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.30,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No, když je to naladěné k náladě, tak asi v pořádku, ale…{Well, setting it to the mood is fine, but...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:55.80,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,No…{Well...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.69,Shirobako_Italics,aru,0,0,0,,Věděla jsem to.{I knew it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.03,Shirobako_Italics,aru,0,0,0,,Věděla jsem, že {I knew that}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.81,Shirobako_Italics,aru,0,0,0,,sestra patří k Gingerům.{Onee-san belonged to Ginger.}{fixme: sestra, sestřička^^^^^^few lines above}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.89,Shirobako_Italics,aru,0,0,0,,Věděla jsem to!{I knew it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:10.87,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.53,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Neladí to?{That's not right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.92,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Neladí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:14.67,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Zkusme něco jiného.{Then let's try something else.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:17.74,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ale ne. Dejte to zpátky.\NOmlouvám se.{Let's go back to the original music. I'm sorry.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.52,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Tak co je tedy špatně?{Then what's not right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:20.93,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Možná je to ta kresba…{Maybe it's the drawings...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:21.82,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Co?!{What?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.72,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No…{m, well...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.60,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Arupinin obličej v téhle scéně je roztomilej, že?{fixme}{Arupin's crying face is cute, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.47,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,No, jo…{Well, yeah.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:32.40,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Nemyslím si ale, že by měl vypadat {\i1}takhle {\i0}roztomile.{But I don't think it's supposed \Nto be this kind of cute.}{fixme}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:33.36,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,„Takhle“?{"This kind"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.86,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Po ranním nahrávání jsem dnes přemýšlel…{I was thinking during this morning's \Nafter-recording session...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.32,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Arupin je ta nejjediněčnější postava,{Arupin's the most unique character,}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.53,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,ale zároveň je tou nejreálnější postavou.{but she's also the most real character.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:43.30,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Myslím, že se bude líbit spíš ženám, než mužům.{I think girls will like her more than guys will.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.26,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,He? Ženám?{Huh? Girls?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.24,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Vážně?{Really?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.52,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Ano! Mně se moc líbí.{Yes! I like her a lot.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.15,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Hmm… aha.{Oh, I see.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.27,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Takže Arupin víc působí na ženy…{So Arupin appeals to girls...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:56.65,Exodus!_11:52_(Ep02),script,0,0,0,,Exodus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:56.65,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Já se snažím v Arupin snažím mít něco trochu jiného, než je v ostatních moe postavách.{The Arupin I'm going for is different \Nfrom other moe characters...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.68,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Rád bych, aby trochu vybočovala.{I'd like her to be a little off.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.98,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Teda, Arupin, kterou jsme teď viděli byla roztomilá,{I mean, the Arupin we just saw was cute,}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:03.06,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,ale zdá se mi, že to nesedí.{but I think it's not quite right.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.03,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Byla snad chyba v mém režírování? {Was my directing wrong?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.53,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ne, nejde o režii…{No, it's not the directing...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.35,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ten problém je spíš ta postava.{I think it's the character that's the problem.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:09.79,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:14.40,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Arupin má nepříjemné vzpomínky na minulost… {Arupin has an annoying side, \Nin that she can't let go of her past...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:16.04,Exodus!(big)_11:52_(Ep02) - Copy,big,0,0,0,,Exodus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.04,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,A myslím, že se ve svých dvaceti{And I don't think she got along}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:19.00,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,s ostatními moc nepohodla.{with others in her early twenties.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.05,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Taky myslím, že byla šikanována,{I think she was also bullied,}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:24.80,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,a vůbec označována za „divnou“.{and had been labeled as \Na little weird all her life...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.12,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,A potom, to byla sestřička,{And then, I think it was Onee-san}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.36,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,která přišla a pomohla jí.{who came in and changed that for her.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:32.79,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Něco jako „Můžu tady zůstat?“\N„Jasňačka!“{Something like, "Can I stay here?" \N"Sure, you can!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.81,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Takže Arupin se se sestřičkou setkala{So Arupin actually met}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.42,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,dřív, než se s ní setkaly Akane a Aja.{Onee-san before Akane or Aya.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.02,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Cože?!{What?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:39.36,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,He…{Huh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:42.67,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Takže si myslím, že ten šok v téhle scéně pro ní byl trošku komplikovanější…{So I think her shock here \Nis a bit more complicated.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.06,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Um, promiňte!{Um, I'm sorry!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.62,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Nepamatuju se, že bych něco takovýho potvrzovala…{I don't think I confirmed that setting...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:49.41,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ah, omlouvám se. To je všechno jen v mé hlavě.{Oh, sorry. That's all just in my head.}
