Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.08,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ne, tak jsem to…{No, I mean...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.46,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Mimo jiné, to říkáš trochu pozdě, ne?{Also, this is a bit late in the game, isn't it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.61,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,He? Pozdě?{Huh? Is it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:59.50,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ale postavy se vyvíjí, když vyvíjíte jejich příběh, ne?{But characters grow while you're \Nmaking their story, don't they?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.59,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Ne, tím chci říct, že {No, I'm saying that trying to make}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.01,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,snažit se udělat nový {setting}SETTING{fixme} postavy nám momentálně akorát přidělá strosti.{a new character setting right now \Nwould make trouble for us.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.80,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Tak? Mám tu hudbu takhle nechat?{So, do we keep the music as is?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:07.50,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Nebo to změnit?{Or change it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.33,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ah, no, změníme kresby.{Oh, we're going to change the drawings.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.54,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,He?! Um,{What?! Um,}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.60,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,myslíte tím doufám jen opravu výrazů?{does that mean we're \Ncorrecting the expressions?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.95,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ne, myslím, že bychom to měli opravit od základu.{No, I think it'd be the acting \Nand everything else, too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:15.98,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Teď hned?!{Starting now?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.72,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Jako třeba, když Arupin zakřičí „Věděla jsem to!“{Like, before Arupin shouts, "I knew it!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.82,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,všechny její emoce nabudou a…{all these conflicting emotions swell up,}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:23.15,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,…její vnitřní chaos zapříčiní její hrubý nádech a…{and the chaos inside makes \Nher breathing coarse, like...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.99,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Um… chcete tím říct, že máme začít\Nzase od klíčové animace?{Um... Does that mean we have to \Nstart over from the key animation?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:30.33,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Eh? Uh, jo. Přesně tak.{Eh? Uh, yeah. I guess that's what it means.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.92,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,To jako vážně?!{Seriously, Director?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.37,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Můžeme udělat maximálně tak krásný stillframe!{We'd have to go with pretty still \Nframes rather than broken animation.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.91,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Krásnou animaci za ten čas, co máme nestihneme!{If we have to fix everything from that \Npoint, we won't make the delivery!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:40.92,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No, prostě to teď nevypadá moc jako Arupin…{Well, the acting just isn't like Arupin...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.17,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Moje režírování je naprosto v pořádku!{I don't think my directing is off at all!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.82,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ano, proto drobnou opravou…{Yes, so with a little correction...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.38,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Tohle není jen drobná oprava!{This isn't just a little correction!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.83,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Režisére,{Director,}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.97,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,vy se nikdy nepoučíte, co?{you do the same thing time \Nand time again, don't you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.06,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Co tím myslíte?{What do you mean by that?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.64,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Copak chcete, aby se zase stalo {\i1}tamto{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:57.57,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No, ale…{Well, th-that was...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.68,Shirobako_Main,sound,0,0,0,,Klid, klid… O tom tu teď mluvit nemusíme…{N-Now, now... We don't have \Nto talk about that now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.50,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Jestli si dobře pamatuju, tak studio, rozpočet,{If I remember correctly, \Nthe studio, the budget,}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.32,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,dokonce i plán byl dost těsnej.{and the schedule were all really tight.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.82,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Ale ten, kdo to minule dodělal jste byl vy, režisére!{But the one who dealt the \Nfinal blow was you, Director!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.75,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,To není…{That's not...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.74,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No, je to pravda, ale…{Well, that is true, but...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.69,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Byl jste tak moc posedlý tím, {You obsessed too much over the fact}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.00,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,že to byla prvotina a zabil jste díky tomu náš plán,{that it was an original and killed our schedule,}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.28,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,což je přesně to samé, co děláte teď!{which is exactly what's going on right now!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.00,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Není to až tak hrozné…{It's not that bad...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.91,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Můj debut režiséra animace{My debut as an animation director was}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:22.40,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,byla ta legendární série,\Nkde byla animace totálně zpackaná!{that legendary series where the \Nanimation was totally wrecked!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.09,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Devátá epizoda {\i1}Nebe Jiggly Jiggly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.54,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Fráze "horší jak Jiggly" a "skoro jak Jiggly" se dokonce staly internetovym slangem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:28.09,Beyond_Shakey_14:24_(Ep02),sign,0,0,0,,"Horší jak Jiggly" je přezdívka 9. epizody seriálu {\i1}Nebe Jiggly Jiggly{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:28.09,Beyond_Shakey_14:24_(Ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(9,8)\fs14}cojávim, tohle animu saje čuraky proboha
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:28.09,A_legend_14:24_(Ep02),defi,0,0,0,,Ve více významech (většinou ve špatném) je legendární. Říká se, že tuhle hovadinu už tahle\Ngenerace ničím nepředčí.\NPouze a jen s příšernými pozadími a nereálnou animací, je význam neznámý. {In various (especially in bad) ways, a legend. It is rumored that nothing will ever beat it in this \Ngeneration. With only creepy backgrounds and surreal booby shaking, the meaning is unknown...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:30.66,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Tyhle termíny budou lidé používat až do konce světa!{Those terms will be spoken now and forever!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.31,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Omlouvám se!{I'm sorry!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.30,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Neomlouvej se!{Don't apologize!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:37.85,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Tak co budem dělat, Nabe-P? Předěláme to, nebo ne?{What are we going to do, Nabe-P? \NAre we going to fix this or not?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.30,Shirobako_Main,nabe,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.56,Shirobako_Main,nabe,0,0,0,,Co myslíš, Mijamori?{What should we do, Miyamori?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.67,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Na to se neptejte mě, Watanabe!{That's asking too much of me, Watanabe-san!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.69,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Teda, je na to vůbec čas? Asi ne, co?{I mean, is there even time? \NThere isn't, is there?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.88,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Máme ještě pět dní.{We have five more days until delivery.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.55,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Když všechno přepočítáme…{If we recalculate things...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:54.03,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,a dneska začneme kreslit klíčové snímky, tak bychom to měli stihnout.{and start the key frames tonight, \Nwe might make it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.38,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Opravdu?!{Really?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:58.63,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Vážně? To jako vážně budem předělávat klíčový snímky?{Seriously? Are we seriously doing \Na retake on the key frames?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:14:59.58,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Nemůžem snad?{Wecan't?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:02.25,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,No, plán kterej mi tu teď říkáš…{The key frame plan you're \Ntelling me right now...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.83,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Nevim, jestli ho zvládnu vysvětlit animátorům, bez toho aniž by mě zmátlili.{I have no confidence that I can \Nexplain it to the key animators.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.88,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.83,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Než začneme předělávat klíčové snímky téhle epizody,{If we're redoing the key frames for this episode,}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.41,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,než začneme s produkcí,{before we go into production,}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.96,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,měli bychom si sednout a promluvit si jetšě jednou o{why don't we all sit down and decide on}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.19,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Arupin a ostatních postavách z {\i1}Exodus{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.66,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Myslím, že je to dost důležité.{I think that's rather important.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:20.81,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,{\fs14\pos(1032,492)\fade(2000,2000)}↓ /širobako/ 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:25.74,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Režisér by vám rád řekl něco důležitého.{The director has something \Nvery important to say.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:29.53,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Mluvení před všemi mi moc nejde.{I'm not really good at speaking \Nin front of everyone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.58,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Říká, že naše interpretace Arupin je zcela špatně.{He's saying that our interpretation \Nof Arupin is completely wrong.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.37,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Neříkám, že je úplně špatně! Jen trochu…{I didn't say it's totally wrong! Just a little.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.29,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Prý bych se měl zlepšit ve svém režírování.{Apparently, we have to completely \Nreconsider our directing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:40.26,Shirobako_Main,honda,0,0,0,,To je docela hnusný, Jamado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.37,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Tos říkal ty!{It's the simple truth.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.61,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Týjo, najednou takový změny!{Talk about a sudden change of events!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.50,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Nejde o to režírování…{It's not about the directing...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.60,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Jen bych rád probral naše chápání daných postav.{I'd just like us to discuss our \Nunderstanding of the characters.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:50.26,Ogasawara_Rinko_15:45_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Ogasawara Rinko \N{\fs22.5}Character Design\NGeneral Animation \NSupervisor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.56,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,To prakticky znamená všechno!{That basically means everything.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:54.26,Iguchi_Yumi_15:50_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Iguči Jumi \N{\fs22.5}General Animation \NSupervisor Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.87,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,He? Fakt?{Huh? It does?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:55.17,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,{You made it sound like we had no choice \Nsince we'd be changing the character.}To ty jsi řekl, že nemáme na vybranou, jelikož budeme měnit postavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.54,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,To jsem řekl?{I did?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:16:02.19,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,No, řekl jste „postavy se vyvíjí, když vyvíjíte jejich příběh.“{It was, "characters grow while}{you're making their story," to be precise.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.48,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Oh, pravda!{That's right!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.75,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Takže, ohledně tohodle,{So, on that note,}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:09.01,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Pokusila jsem se dát dohromady chronologii{I tried putting together chronologies and}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:08.82,Akane_16:07_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Akane
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:08.82,Musashino_Animation_(Ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Musašino Animation{Musashino Animation}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:09.74,Aya16:07_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Aja
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:09.74,Musashino_Animation_(Ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Musašino Animation{Musashino Animation}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:10.65,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,a historii daných postav.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:10.65,Arupin_16:07_(ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Arupin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:10.65,Musashino_Animation_(Ep02),sign,0,0,0,,Musašino Animation{Musashino Animation}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.77,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,He? Akane byla na dívčí škole?{Huh? Did Akane come from an all-girls' school?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:23.12,Three_girls'_names_16:10_(Ep02),sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H519FCD&}Arupin                    {\c&H6940CF&}Akane                        {\c&H925B56&}Aya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:14.92,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Je to zmíněno v páté epizodě.{They mention it in episode five.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.07,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Oh, dobrá.{Oh, right.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:19.78,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Světu se říká, že Arupin je 17, ale ve skutečnosti je jí 29.{Arupin's publicized age is seventeen, \Nbut she's actually twenty-nine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:23.12,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Také konstatovala, že se chtěla stát idolem, aby vydělala hodně peněz.{She has declared that she became \Nan idol to make a lot of money.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.15,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Ale zdá se mi, že ona je centrem všech dramatických událostí,{But I believe that she is the center \Nof all of the dramatic events,}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:29.26,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,jako třeba, že byla první, kdo našel manažerovo tělo a taky byla cílem únosu.{like finding their manager's body first \Nand being kidnapped by the enemy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.53,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Jo. A já myslím,{Right. And I think}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:33.38,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,že to jsme právě trochu přehnali.{we used that a bit too much.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.18,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Rád bych, aby trochu prozkoumala sebe sama.{I'd like for us to explore \Nher inner self a bit more.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.15,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Sebe sama?{Her inner self?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:40.97,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No, pro začátek, co třeba zvýšit trochu její inteligenci.{For starters, you know, maybe \Nraise her intelligence a little bit...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:44.34,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Cože? Ale Arupin je skvělá kvůli své stupiditě!{What? But Arupin's great \Nbecause of her stupidity.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:47.74,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No, její stupidita je v pořádku, ale zase má vždycky největší tušení, co se děje…{Well, stupid is fine, but she also \Nunderstands what's going on the most.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:50.52,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Právě v téhle epizodě je odhalena důležitá část děje,{Apparently, a very important \Nplot point is going to be revealed}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:52.61,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,kdy je odhaleno, že Arupin potkala sestřičku už v minulosti.{where Arupin had known Onee-san in her past.}{fixme sestřičku}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.91,Shirobako_Main,all,0,0,0,,Cože?!{What?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.91,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Vážně?!{Seriously?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:56.31,Shirobako_Main,honda,0,0,0,,Nepozmění to dost poslední epizodu?{Is this something that'll affect the final episode?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:58.34,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Tím si teď nejsem jist. Promiň.{Uh, I'm not sure. Sorry.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.71,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Vážně bych to rád dokázal líp vysvětlit.{I really wish I could explain it better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:04.19,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Posuzovat, rozhodovat a všem ta\Nrozhodnutí předat je přesěně práce režiséra.{To judge, make decisions, and relay \Nthem to everyone is a director's job.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.66,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,To já chápu, ale…{I understand that, but...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:08.36,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Existují i režiséři, co se neumí moc vyjádřit.{There are also directors who \Naren't very good at speaking.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.01,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,To je ten důvod, proč ses rozvedl?{Is that why you got divorced?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:10.86,Shirobako_Main,both,0,0,0,,Cože?!{What?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.67,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,Neustále nechávat svou manželku osamotě{If you keep leaving your nice wife alone}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:17.20,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,a pak říkát „Myslel jsem, že to pochopí“ je jako šlapat na minu.{and saying, "I thought she'd understand," \Nit's like stepping on a land mine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.99,Shirobako_Main,yano,0,0,0,,Ale copak? Zní to jako něco, co praktikuješ?{Oh? Does that hit close to home?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:20.89,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Ne, vůbec ne!{No, not at all!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.79,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Jak to víš, Iguči?!{Iguchi-san, how did you know?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:24.57,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,Zmiňuješ to pokaždé, když se opiješ.{You mention it every time you drink.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.66,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ale néé!{You're kidding!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.23,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,Slyšela jsem to tolikrát, až mě z toho bolí uši.{I've heard it so many times, my ears hurt.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:31.23,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ty vole, to si vůbec nepamatuju.{Holy crap, I don't remember that at all.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:31.23,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,{\a6}Wow, nasral si manželku, tak si dostal rozvodový papíry? To je drsný.{You got divorce papers because you \Npissed off your wife? That's harsh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:34.28,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Byl to klidnej rozvod! Dokonce jsem i zaplatil vyrovnání!{t was a peaceful divorce! \NI even paid a settlement!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.74,Shirobako_Main,yano,0,0,0,,Myslim, že tohle nepotřebujem slyšet.{I don't think we really \Nwant to hear about that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.57,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,V každém případě, vyslechněte mě!{Anyway, just hear me out!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:41.02,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Můžeš přísahat, že už nic znenadání nezměníš?{Can you guarantee you won't \Nsuddenly change things on us again?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.11,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Můžu!{I can!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:42.87,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Myslim…{I think...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.72,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Vidíte?!{See?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.99,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Tohle bude hustý! Něco jako {\i1}Jiggly Jiggly Nebe: Návrat{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.40,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Bude to hit!{It'll be a hit!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:50.42,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,To není hit! Kdo by si vůbec myslel, že to byl hit?{It's not a hit! Who would think it's a hit?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.62,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Přece občané internetu?{The citizens of the internet?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.25,Shirobako_Main,yano,0,0,0,,Ale ty se koukaj jen na net, ne?!{Don't they only look at the internet?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:53.72,Shirobako_Main,,0,0,0,,Díky.{Thank you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.71,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Nekoukaj jen na net!{Not only the internet!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:55.89,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Nebudu se dívat na net!{I won't look at the internet!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:58.62,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Rozhodl jsem se, že už se po tom incidentu nikdy nepodívam na net.{I decided that I'd never look at \Nthe internet after that incident.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:17:59.95,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Už nikdy!{Never again!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:03.14,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Mimochodem, tohle je asi dost blbá otázka,{By the way, this might be \Na very simple question,}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:07.14,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,ale má Arupin radši donuty nebo jókan?{but does Arupin prefer donuts or youkan?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.81,Shirobako_Main,yano,0,0,0,,Eh, jak tě takováhle otázka teď tak najednou napadla?{Uh, where'd that multiple-choice \Nquestion come from?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:13.37,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,No, její krevní typ, výšku i váhu už jsme rozhodli,{Well, her blood type, height, \Nand weight have been decided,}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:16.04,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,ale myslím, že jsme se ještě neshodli na tom, co má ráda.{but I don't think her favorite \Nthings have been decided yet.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.41,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Osobně doufám, že má radši donuty.{Personally, I hope she prefers donuts.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:21.46,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Arupin má ráda jahodový koláč!{Arupin likes strawberry shortcake!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.26,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Neříkáte to náhodou proto, že je\Nměla ráda vaše žen— Au…{Is that because your wife liked them— Ow...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:25.12,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Jahodový koláč je až moc klišé.{Strawberry shortcake is too cliché.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:26.62,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,To vůbec nevadí!{It's fine that it's cliché!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.79,Shirobako_Main,honda,0,0,0,,Podlemě je to v pořádku.{I think it's fine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:31.31,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,To vůbec nezapříčiní aby ta postava vynikla. Dejte jí aspoň dorajaki.{That definitely won't make the character \Nstand out. At least make it dorayaki.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:32.85,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,A co si myslíš, že Arupin je? Kočičí robot?!{What is she? A cat robot?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:34.09,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,No, dorajaki k ní sedí, ne?{Well, it sounds like Arupin, doesn't it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.83,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Arupin nemá ráda sladké.{Arupin doesn't eat sweets.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.09,Shirobako_Main,person,0,0,0,,Souhlasím, přece jen jí už je 29.{I agree. She's twenty-nine, after all.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.42,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Jí sladkosti, {\i1}protože {\i0}jí je 29.{She eats them, becuse she's twenty-nine}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:44.16,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Je to ten osobností typ, co rád jahodu sní až na konci.{She's the type to eat the strawberry last!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:44.16,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,{\a9\fs16\pos(14,13)}what the fuck am i doing with my life; i am so fucking shit at translating, jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.45,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,Rejžo, vy jste tak naplněn sny.{You're so filled with dreams, Director.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.74,Shirobako_Main,kinon,0,0,0,,Iguči, jsi na mě až moc zlá!{Iguchi-san, you're way too harsh on me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.32,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,Myslíš?{You think so?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.65,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Ah, ale…{Oh, but...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.74,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Co má člověk rád ukazuje jeho osobnost, ne?{What a person likes reveals \Ntheir personality, doesn't it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:56.19,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Jestli má ráda donuty, tak se k ní můžu přirovnat,{he likes donuts, I can totally relate to her,}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.15,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,jako kdyby byla mým soudruhem.{like she's a comrade.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.46,Shirobako_Main,erika,0,0,0,,Moc to nechápu, Mijamori.{I'm not getting it, Myamori.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.20,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,No…{Um...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.12,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,A co třeba něco překvapivýho\Njako třeba sušené rejnočí ploutve?!{How about something surprising \Nlike dried stingray fins?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.95,Shirobako_Main,yamada,0,0,0,,To by víc sedělo k Ájince!{It'd be Ayachin who likes those.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.64,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Ájin… ce?{Aya... "chin"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.42,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Jo. Zbožňuju Aju. Nějaký problém?!{Yeah, that's right. I'm rooting \Nfor Ayachin. Is that a problem?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.14,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Není divu, že si s ní dal větší práci.{No wonder you seemed \Nto work harder with her.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.94,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Ájinka se v budoucnosti stane vášnivým pijanem.{Ayachin's destined to become \Na heavy drinker in the future.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.59,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Úplně bych se miloval s ní jen tak popíjet!{I'd love to have a drink with her!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.34,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Jo jo, plně souhlasím!{Yeah, I totally get that!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.65,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,He? Nemá to bejt náhodou moe animu?{Huh? Isn't this a moe anime?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.71,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ájinka držící láhev saké by byla dost moe.{If Ayachin were holding a bottle of sake, \NI think that'd be pretty moe.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.00,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Jo, to je dost moe.{Yeah, that's totally moe.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.06,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,Moe sem, moe tam…{Moe this, moe that...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:27.77,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Mrtvý slovo.{It's a dead word.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.32,Shirobako_Main,honda,0,0,0,,Jo, nejsem si tim jistej…{Yeah, I'm not sure about that...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.25,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,{\a6}Ne, moe zažívá comeback! Moe je určitě zpět!{No, it's totally making a comeback. \NMoe's definitely back.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:33.19,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Hej, Iguči je na naší straně!{Hey, Iguchi-san's on our side.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.82,Shirobako_Main,both,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}＼(^o^)／
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:38.08,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Akane sice nepije, ale podle mě by se i tak přidala.{Akane doesn't drink, but she \Nseems like she'd still hang out.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:40.36,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,A Arupin je ten typ, co po trošce alkoholu hned usne.{Arupin's the type to immediately fall asleep.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:43.16,Shirobako_Main,yamada,0,0,0,,V dobrém i ve zlém, její obrana je chabá.{For better or worse, her defenses are weak.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:43.16,Shirobako_Main,yamada,0,0,0,,{\a9\pos(18,21)\fs14}fuck this anime, fuck this translation, fuck me, fuck everything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.40,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Přesně!{Exactly!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:48.32,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Proto si postupně uvědomuje, že je sestřička zradila,{That's why she gradually realizes \Nthat Onee-san betrayed them,}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:50.15,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,ale nemůže to ostatním říct.{but she can't tell the other two.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:54.12,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Po tom, co jsme probrali Arupin a její city prostě…{After thinking about Arupin \Nand her feelings, I just...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.21,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Já prsotě…{I just...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:58.40,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Když Arupin říká „Věděla jsem to,“{When Arupin says, "I knew it,"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.27,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Myslím, že to chce nějakou takovouhle emoci,{I think it needs to be packed \Nwith every kind of emotion,}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.68,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,a k tomu jejich celý příběh a všechny chvilky, které společně sdílely. {along with their whole story \Nand all the time they shared.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.03,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Něco takového nejde sdělit jen krásným obličejem!{There's no way she could say \Nthat with just a pretty face.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:10.03,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Chce to aby byla uvnitř více zamotaná a zničená!{She needs to be more scrambled \Nand messed up on the inside!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.19,Shirobako_Main,endou,0,0,0,,Takže má vypadat ošklivě, když to říká?{You mean she needs to look \Nugly when she says it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.75,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,He? Nejsou ošklivé obličeje moe?{HHuh? But aren't ugly faces moe?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.30,Shirobako_Main,endo,0,0,0,,Eh, nemyslím si…{Uh, I don't know about that...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.15,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,To by bylo dost hustý.{That'd be pretty hardcore.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.37,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No, necítíte nic, když předtím, než se rozbrečí,{Before she starts crying, \Ndoesn't seeing her nostrils flare}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.64,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,vidíte její obličej naplněný vráskami, zatímco se naplňuje emocemi?{or the way her face wrinkles as the \Nemotions well up make you feel something?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.12,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Nevim, nevim…{Does it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.75,Shirobako_Main,honda,0,0,0,,Timhle ale úplně přestáváme myslet na diváky…{We might end up leaving \Nthe audience behind...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.26,Shirobako_Main,mado,0,0,0,,A nebo je úplně vyděsíme.{Or just scare them off completely.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:32.30,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Bude to v pohodě! Úplně tim diváky uneseme!{It'll be fine! We're going to kidnap \Nthem, not leave them behind!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:33.86,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Prostě vžum.{Like, swoop!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.87,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,To se lehko řekne.{It's easier said than done.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:39.26,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Jo, to je pravda…{Well, yeah, that's true...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.90,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ale výrazy plné symbolismu časem přestanou bavit, ať už jsou jakkoliv pěkné!{But expressions filled with symbolism \Nget boring, however pretty they are!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:45.10,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Je to výzva! Věřte si na úplně novém levelu!{Challenge! Challenge yourself to new horizons!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.35,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Novém levelu, huh…{New horizons, huh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.81,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Má animace snad být jen podle nějaké šablony? Samozřejmě, že ne!{Is animation the classic example of being \Nconfined to some template? Of course not!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.14,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Animace znamená, že něčemu dáváme život!{It means we're breathing life into something!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.51,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Ale vy nejste ten, co to bude kreslit, rejžo.{But you're not the one \Ndrawing everything, Director.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.73,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,No, to je pravda… Ale i tak!{Well, that's true... But still!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:01.31,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Arupin je sice trochu hloupoučká a né–moc talentovaná, ale je citlivá a bojí se o ostatní.{Arupin's a bit stupid and not very talented, \Nbut she's delicate, and concerned.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:04.57,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Chci vystihnout všechnu její složitost!{I want to express all of her complexities!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:07.92,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Arupin je tady!{Arupin is right here!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.68,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Je tady, ne?{She's here, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:12.21,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,He?{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.41,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Je tady, ne?!{She's here, right?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:13.92,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,Cože?{bWhat?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:14.79,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Je přímo tu, že jo?!{She's here, right?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:18.00,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Ano! Arupin je přímo mezi námi!{bYes! Arupin is already right here!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.41,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Vidíte? Jen jí musíme…{See? We just have to}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:22.24,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,vytvarovat!{make it take shape!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:23.97,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Říkáte „jen,“ ale…{You say "just," but...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.92,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,To zvládneme! Pojďme na to!{We can do it! Please make this happen!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:26.84,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Pojďme na to!{Let's do it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:30.25,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Pojďme přivést Arupin k životu… do tohoto…{Let's bring Arupin into life... into this...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.91,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,dovolme ji přijít… nechme ji zůstat v tomto světě?{let her be in... let her stay in this world?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:34.14,Shirobako_Main,yano,0,0,0,,Uklidni se!{Calm down!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.27,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,To je jedno,{Anyway,}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:37.31,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,Arupin je tady!{Arupin is here!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:43.83,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,{\fade(2000,2000)\fs16\pos(243,21)}HÓLY–ŠIT–SUDDENLY–LE–MAGIC–SCI-FI-SOMETHING–CO–SE–TO–KURVA–VŮBEC–DĚJE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:22:02.83,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0,0,0,,{\fade(2000,2000)\fs16\pos(164,19)}najednou tlustý faggoti maj svoje waifu… k. 10/10 animu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:14.98,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Dobrá…{All right...}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:15.85,Shirobako_Main,honda,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:18.80,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,Jsem si jistej, že Ogasawara a Iguči to zvládnou.{I'm sure Ogasawara-san \Nand Iguchi-san can do this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:21.54,Shirobako_Main,yama,0,0,0,,I když musím říct, že současný plán je docela kulervoucí.{Though the schedule... is a bit tight.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:22.45,Shirobako_Main,honda,0,0,0,,„Docela“?!{"A bit"?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:24.75,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,Takže já to mám nakreslit{Does that mean I'll be drawing them}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:27.29,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0,0,0,,a Ogasawara bude mít na starost animaci?{and Ogasawara-san will be \Nthe animation supervisor?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:28.61,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Prosím.{Please.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:29.37,Shirobako_Main,kino,0,0,0,,Ano?{Okay?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:32.00,Shirobako_Main,ogasa,0,0,0,,Rozumím.{Understood.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:37.33,Shirobako_Main,boss,0,0,0,,Udělal jsem moc takojaki.\N Nechcete trochu?{I made too much takoyaki. \NWould you all like some?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:38.37,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Jasňačka!{Heck, yeah!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:41.63,Shirobako_Main,taro,0,0,0,,Ahhh, to je horký!{Ow, that's hot!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:45.93,Shirobako_Main,ogasa,0,0,0,,Mijamori,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:47.88,Shirobako_Main,ogasa,0,0,0,,přines mi prosím ten střih.{please bring me that cut.}
